'''伊斯塔帕'''（{{lang-es|Iztapa}}）是[[危地馬拉|危地馬拉]]的一个城鎮，位于[[埃斯昆特拉省|埃斯昆特拉省]]。面積328平方公里，海拔为1米。2014年人口61448人<ref name="population-Data.org"></ref>，人口密度为每平方公里187.34人。

==历史==
1897年，政府决定在伊斯塔帕修建港口，以减轻[[圣何塞港|圣何塞港]]的运输压力。但在同年9月，政府实施{{tsl|en|Exposición Centroamericana|中美洲博览会}}与跨洋铁路项目失败以后，白银与咖啡的国际价格突然暴跌，这使得危地马拉全国陷入了沉重的经济危机，而时任总统的{{tsl|en|José María Reina Barrios|何塞·玛利亚·雷纳·巴里奥斯}}将他的任期延长至了1902年，这一举措最终导致其被杀{{refn|group=lower-alpha|Back then, the [[巴拿马运河|巴拿马运河]] had not been built yet and Reina Barrios had high hopes on getting international investors interested in the interoceanic railroad, which was the main event for the {{tsl|en|Exposición Centroamericana||Central American Expo}}; unfortunately, due to the economic crisis, and bad budgeting, the government could not complete the railroad and after the failure of the Expo, it had to take drastic austerity measures that included closing schools<ref>{{cite book|last=Arévalo Martínez|first=Rafael|authorlink=Rafael Arévalo Martínez|title=¡Ecce Pericles!|publisher=Tipografía Nacional|location=Guatemala|url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/190285559/Arevalo-Martinez-Ecce-Pericles#scribd|year=1945|language=es|ref=harv|access-date=2019-01-18|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121083736/https://www.scribd.com/doc/190285559/Arevalo-Martinez-Ecce-Pericles#scribd|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}，同时修建港口的计划亦因此搁置。 
伊斯塔帕曾用名Ystapa（与伊斯塔帕发音相近）<ref name=Baily2>{{cite book|last=Baily|first=John|title=Central America; Describing Each of the States of Guatemala, Honduras, Salvador, Nicaragua, and Costa Rica|year=1850|publisher=Trelawney Saunders|location=London|page=77|url=http://www.wdl.org/en/item/7306/view/1/77/|access-date=2019-01-18|archive-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112130735/https://www.wdl.org/en/item/7306/view/1/77/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

